welcome_message_body: "Welcome to charming Bayonet Point! Known for its beautiful beaches and friendly locals, we invite you to explore and enjoy all this lovely city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Executive Airport handles all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Executive Airport caters to high-end clients and offers exclusive amenities.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A at Tampa International Airport serves domestic flights for airlines such as Delta and United.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C at Tampa International Airport serves domestic and international flights for airlines such as American and British Airways.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St. Petersburg-Clearwater International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Gates Terminal
terminals.description: The gates terminal at St. Petersburg-Clearwater International Airport is where passengers board and disembark from their flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport is used exclusively for military flights and operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport offers a small but efficient space for passengers to check-in, pass through security, and access various amenities.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: For those traveling on private or chartered flights, the private terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport offers a comfortable and exclusive experience.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport by connecting to the TPF-WiFi network.
